<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/650348--is-this-a-stand-alone-book-or-do-you-need">-Is this a stand-alone book or do you need to read the previous books to understand the plot here? 
-Is this book sort of like the Indiana Jones adventures?
-Is it well written? I read the In.Jones books and I felt the language was too simple and it did not help to create a very compelling story...
Thanks</a>
</div>
